WEBVTT

00:56.143 --> 00:59.581
HMM. I GOT
YOUR COFFEE.

01:01.670 --> 01:03.715
ARE WE GONNA
TALK ABOUT THIS?

01:03.759 --> 01:05.848
I'M LATE. TRAFFIC'S
ALREADY A MESS.

01:05.891 --> 01:07.458
DAVID, COME ON.

01:07.502 --> 01:10.026
HAVE YOU SEEN MY KEYS?

01:10.070 --> 01:11.680
THEY'RE IN YOUR HAND.

01:13.464 --> 01:15.249
I--
STOP.

01:17.251 --> 01:19.035
HOW ARE YOU FEELING?

01:19.079 --> 01:21.472
UM, I DON'T--I DON'T KNOW
WHEN I'LL BE HOME.

01:21.516 --> 01:22.952
DON'T WAIT UP.

01:46.149 --> 01:48.369
HELLO, SIR. HI.

01:48.412 --> 01:49.805
HEY.

01:51.372 --> 01:53.200
UH, WHEN DO THE BANDAGES
COME OFF?

01:53.243 --> 01:55.376
THE DOC SAYS A WEEK.

01:55.419 --> 01:57.204
HOW ARE YOU DOING?

01:57.247 --> 01:59.597
GOOD. I'M GOOD.

02:03.471 --> 02:05.342
I THINK HE'S BEEN HERE
ALL WEEKEND.

02:11.522 --> 02:13.220
SHOULD HAVE SEEN IT.

02:13.263 --> 02:15.483
SHOULD HAVE SEEN IT.
WHY DIDN'T I SEE IT?

02:17.702 --> 02:20.705
HOW MUCH SLEEP HAVE YOU
GOTTEN SINCE WE GOT BACK?

02:20.749 --> 02:22.098
IT WAS RIGHT THERE.

02:22.142 --> 02:23.317
IT WAS RIGHT THERE,
AND I DIDN'T SEE IT.

02:23.360 --> 02:24.535
NONE OF US DID.

02:26.711 --> 02:29.323
HOW ARE YOU DOING?

02:29.366 --> 02:31.281
FINE.

02:39.855 --> 02:42.031
NOT YOU, TOO.

02:42.074 --> 02:44.033
YOU'RE TIRED OF
PEOPLE ASKING YOU

02:44.076 --> 02:45.513
HOW YOU'RE DOING?

02:47.428 --> 02:49.473
YES, I AM.

02:49.517 --> 02:52.302
DO YOU KNOW WHAT THIS IS?

02:52.346 --> 02:56.045
IT'S AN OPEN INVESTIGATION.
THAT'S ALL.

02:56.088 --> 02:59.222
WE LOST THE FIRST TIME, BUT
WE'LL GET ANOTHER CHANCE.

02:59.266 --> 03:00.484
YES, WE WILL.

03:00.528 --> 03:02.399
THIS TEAM DOESN'T
TAKE CARE OF ME.

03:02.443 --> 03:05.707
I TAKE CARE OF THEM.
THAT'S MY JOB.

03:05.750 --> 03:09.145
MAYBE IT'S BECAUSE
YOU DO THAT JOB SO WELL,

03:09.189 --> 03:11.582
WE WANT TO BE THERE
FOR YOU WHEN WE CAN.

03:13.280 --> 03:16.544
YOU WENT THROUGH
SOMETHING TERRIBLE
OUT THERE,

03:16.587 --> 03:18.633
BUT YOU CAN'T KEEP IT
BOTTLED UP.

03:18.676 --> 03:20.548
YOU KNOW THAT.

03:20.591 --> 03:23.942
SO, DAVE, THERE'S REALLY
ONLY ONE QUESTION,

03:23.986 --> 03:27.163
AND IT'S NOT
"HOW ARE YOU DOING?"

03:27.207 --> 03:29.383
IT'S, WHO DO YOU
TRUST ENOUGH

03:29.426 --> 03:32.647
TO SAY "I'M NOT
DOING SO GOOD"?

03:41.351 --> 03:43.092
WHAT HAPPENED?

03:45.529 --> 03:48.489
I GOT SENT HOME BY
THE PRINCIPAL.

03:50.317 --> 03:52.536
YOU READY TO TALK
ABOUT IT?

04:29.443 --> 04:31.488
ROSSI, VOICE-OVER:
I COULDN'T BREATHE.

04:33.969 --> 04:36.450
I COULDN'T BREATHE.

04:36.493 --> 04:37.886
I'M HERE.

04:41.542 --> 04:42.934
I'M HERE.

05:29.111 --> 05:30.068
THANKS.

05:31.069 --> 05:35.335
AH. IT'S PORTIA.

05:35.378 --> 05:37.511
SO HOW IS
MY SOON-TO-BE

05:37.554 --> 05:39.121
STEPDAUGHTER DOING?

05:39.164 --> 05:41.689
SHE LIKES TO SHARE
QUOTES WITH ME.

05:41.732 --> 05:43.343
HERE'S TODAY'S.

05:43.386 --> 05:45.910
STEPHEN KING WROTE,

05:45.954 --> 05:50.524
"THE MOST IMPORTANT THINGS
ARE THE HARDEST TO SAY."

05:50.567 --> 05:55.485
HOW WEIRDLY APPROPRIATE.

05:57.531 --> 05:58.836
COME ON.

05:58.880 --> 06:01.230
WE ARE GETTING MARRIED
IN 3 WEEKS.

06:01.273 --> 06:04.015
AND IF WE WANT THIS TO WORK,

06:04.059 --> 06:06.453
YOU HAVE TO LET ME IN.

06:11.371 --> 06:13.416
IT STARTED WHEN WE
GOT CALLED IN

06:13.460 --> 06:14.852
ON A SINGLE.

06:14.896 --> 06:16.419
A SINGLE HOMICIDE

06:16.463 --> 06:18.247
IN NASHVILLE, TENNESSEE.

06:18.290 --> 06:20.684
THAT IS, FIREFIGHTERS
RESPONDED TO A HOUSE FIRE

06:20.728 --> 06:22.207
IN THE GREEN HILLS
NEIGHBORHOOD

06:22.251 --> 06:23.818
AND WERE ABLE
TO PUT OUT THE FIRE

06:23.861 --> 06:25.559
BEFORE IT DESTROYED
EVERYTHING,

06:25.602 --> 06:28.953
BUT THEY DISCOVERED THE BODY
OF MONICA FEINSTEIN,

06:28.997 --> 06:30.912
WITH A COMPLETE FACE LIFT.

06:30.955 --> 06:32.348
AND I'M NOT TALKING ABOUT
THE KIND THAT YOU NEED

06:32.392 --> 06:33.567
A WEEKEND AND A BOTTLE OF
ASPIRIN TO GET OVER.

06:33.610 --> 06:35.438
I'M TALKING CHEEK TO CHEEK,
NECK TO NOGGIN.

06:35.482 --> 06:38.833
HER WHOLE FACE WAS LIFTED,
LIKE, REMOVED FROM HER--

06:38.876 --> 06:40.443
LEWIS: ALL RIGHT.
WELL, BURNS ON THE BODY

06:40.487 --> 06:42.619
WERE LIMITED
TO THE LEGS AND FEET,

06:42.663 --> 06:45.622
BUT KNIFE MARKS WENT
ALL THE WAY DOWN
TO THE SKULL.

06:45.666 --> 06:46.841
POSSIBLY SYMBOLIC.

06:46.884 --> 06:48.277
WERE THE CUTS
POSTMORTEM?

06:48.320 --> 06:49.713
THEY WERE. CAUSE OF DEATH
WAS STRANGULATION.

06:49.757 --> 06:51.976
SO THE FACE IS
A TROPHY.

06:52.020 --> 06:53.978
HE TOOK IT WITH HIM
TO RELIVE WHAT HE DID.

06:54.022 --> 06:55.589
REID: AS WITH
JEFFREY DAHMER,

06:55.632 --> 06:56.590
KILLERS OFTEN COLLECT
BODY PARTS

06:56.633 --> 06:58.156
TO COMBAT A FEELING
OF INADEQUACY.

06:58.200 --> 07:00.681
THEY SEE THE TROPHY
AS AN EXTENSION OF
THEIR OWN IDENTITY,

07:00.724 --> 07:02.291
SOMETHING THEY'D RATHER DIE
THAN GIVE UP.

07:02.334 --> 07:03.814
HOW DID THE UNSUB
SET THE FIRE?

07:03.858 --> 07:08.079
GARCIA: FIREFIGHTERS SOURCED
THE FLAMES TO A LIT STOVE

07:08.123 --> 07:11.169
AND THEN DISCOVERED EVIDENCE
OF CORRODED GAS PIPES.

07:11.213 --> 07:12.867
THE GAS PIPES ARE MADE OF
GALVANIZED STEEL,

07:12.910 --> 07:15.478
AND THE HOUSE IS ONLY
A FEW YEARS OLD.

07:15.522 --> 07:17.088
THE UNSUB COULD'VE USED
SULFURIC ACID

07:17.132 --> 07:18.655
TO MIMIC THE EFFECTS
OF CORROSION.

07:18.699 --> 07:19.874
YEAH, HE'S GONE TO
GREAT LENGTHS

07:19.917 --> 07:21.484
TO MAKE THE FIRE
LOOK LIKE
AN ACCIDENT.

07:21.528 --> 07:23.268
NO FORENSIC COUNTERMEASURE.

07:23.312 --> 07:25.488
BURNING THE HOUSE DOWN
WOULD BE A PERFECT WAY
TO COVER YOUR TRACKS.

07:25.532 --> 07:27.490
THE SOPHISTICATION SUGGESTS
THIS ISN'T HIS FIRST,

07:27.534 --> 07:29.013
AND HE'S PROBABLY
PLANNING MORE.

07:29.057 --> 07:30.667
WHEELS UP IN 20.

07:31.842 --> 07:34.454
DID YOU FIND ANY OTHER
VICTIMS?

07:34.497 --> 07:36.020
NOT ON THE FIRST SWEEP.

07:37.369 --> 07:39.633
SO WE DISCUSSED
WHAT WE KNEW

07:39.676 --> 07:41.286
ON OUR WAY
TO NASHVILLE.

07:43.071 --> 07:45.639
MONICA FEINSTEIN, 52.

07:45.682 --> 07:47.684
TAUGHT PRESCHOOL,
VOLUNTEERED IN
A SOUP KITCHEN.

07:47.728 --> 07:48.946
SINGLE MOM, ADULT SON.

07:48.990 --> 07:50.731
ABOUT AS LOW-RISK A LIFESTYLE
AS YOU CAN GET.

07:50.774 --> 07:52.254
PRENTISS: AND THERE'S
NO SIGN OF FORCED ENTRY,

07:52.297 --> 07:54.648
SO, THE UNSUB WAS EITHER
SOMEONE SHE KNEW

07:54.691 --> 07:56.040
OR DIDN'T SEE AS A THREAT.

07:56.084 --> 07:57.607
HE SETS THE FIRE TO
DESTROY THE EVIDENCE,

07:57.651 --> 07:59.000
BUT HE COULD ALSO BE
SETTING IT

07:59.043 --> 08:00.218
TO HIDE HIS OWN SHAME
OR DISGUST

08:00.262 --> 08:01.524
FOR HAVING TAKEN
THE FACE.

08:01.568 --> 08:02.699
YEAH, THAT'S TRUE,

08:02.743 --> 08:03.961
BUT EVEN IF IT WAS
A TROPHY,

08:04.005 --> 08:05.746
HE MIGHT'VE
HATED HIMSELF
FOR WANTING IT.

08:05.789 --> 08:07.617
ROSSI: MOST UNSUBS HAVE
A LOVE-HATE RELATIONSHIP

08:07.661 --> 08:08.966
WITH THEIR COMPULSIONS.

08:09.010 --> 08:10.925
WHICH IN THIS CASE WOULD BE
EROTOPHONOPHILIA.

08:10.968 --> 08:12.927
KRYSTALL:
EROTOPHONO-WHAT?

08:12.970 --> 08:15.538
IT'S A $10 WORD
FOR LUST MURDER.

08:15.582 --> 08:17.540
IT INVOLVES THE MUTILATION
OF BODY PARTS

08:17.584 --> 08:19.324
THE UNSUB FINDS MOST
ATTRACTIVE.

08:19.368 --> 08:22.153
NOW, IT COULD BE FEET
OR KNEECAPS,

08:22.197 --> 08:24.939
BUT IT'S USUALLY
BREASTS OR GENITAL--

08:24.982 --> 08:26.506
OK, GOT IT. GOT IT.

08:26.549 --> 08:27.724
YOU ASKED.
OK, WELL,

08:27.768 --> 08:28.943
YOU KNOW, MAYBE WE
SHOULD HAVE

08:28.986 --> 08:30.161
A SAFE WORD
OR SOMETHING.

08:30.205 --> 08:31.728
MAYBE YOU SHOULD
JUST TELL ME

08:31.772 --> 08:34.383
WHEN TO LEAVE SOMETHING
TO THE IMAGINATION.

08:34.426 --> 08:36.559
DEAL. OK.

08:36.603 --> 08:41.303
SO IN THIS CASE,
IT WAS THE FACE. WHY?

08:41.346 --> 08:44.785
THAT'S THE QUESTION
WE PURSUED WHEN WE LANDED.

08:50.225 --> 08:51.835
SIMMONS: ACCORDING
TO THE AUTOPSY,

08:51.879 --> 08:54.751
THE CUTS ON MONICA
WERE ROUGH
AND IMPRECISE.

08:54.795 --> 08:56.971
BUT HE HAD
ALREADY STRANGLED HER.

08:57.014 --> 08:58.668
HE HAD THE TIME AND CONTROL
TO DO WHAT HE WANTS.

08:58.712 --> 08:59.843
HE HAD NO REASON TO RUSH.

08:59.887 --> 09:01.845
BASED ON HIS SKILL
AND ORGANIZATION,

09:01.889 --> 09:03.543
IT'S NOT INEXPERIENCE.

09:03.586 --> 09:05.153
IT COULD BE THAT
HE LOSES CONTROL

09:05.196 --> 09:06.850
BECAUSE HE'S OBTAINED
GRATIFICATION.

09:06.894 --> 09:08.591
A DOPAMINE RUSH
IS SIMILAR
TO DRUG ADDICTION,

09:08.635 --> 09:11.463
WHERE A FEELING OF
EUPHORIA SUSPENDS
FINE MOTOR SKILLS.

09:11.507 --> 09:12.987
PRENTISS: MONICA FEINSTEIN
HAS A GROWN SON?

09:13.030 --> 09:15.772
YEAH, CARL,
AGE 19. HE GOES TO
TENNESSEE TECH.

09:15.816 --> 09:17.295
PRENTISS:
LET'S BRING HIM IN.

09:17.339 --> 09:18.645
IF THE UNSUB WAS SOMEBODY
MONICA KNEW,

09:18.688 --> 09:20.908
HE MIGHT BE ABLE
TO GIVE US A SUSPECT.

09:25.913 --> 09:28.524
YEAH. I KNOW EXACTLY
WHO DID THIS.

09:28.568 --> 09:32.223
HIS NAME'S MAC.
HE, UH--

09:32.267 --> 09:34.008
HE WAS DATING MY MOM.

09:34.051 --> 09:35.836
WHAT CAN YOU TELL ME
ABOUT HIM?

09:35.879 --> 09:37.838
DORKY, BORING.

09:39.013 --> 09:40.841
HE ALWAYS WORE
THESE, UH--

09:40.884 --> 09:43.321
THESE
WOOL SWEATERS.

09:43.365 --> 09:44.888
HE NEVER
STAYED OVER.

09:44.932 --> 09:46.673
HE SAID HE WANTED
TO PROTECT

09:46.716 --> 09:48.326
MY MOTHER'S VIRTUE.

09:48.370 --> 09:50.807
THE KIND OF GUY THAT
WOULD GO OUT OF HIS WAY

09:50.851 --> 09:52.635
TO APPEAR NONTHREATENING?

09:52.679 --> 09:53.984
YEAH.

09:54.028 --> 09:57.248
YOU WENT RIGHT AFTER HIM
AS YOUR MOTHER'S KILLER.

09:57.292 --> 09:59.033
HOW COME?

09:59.076 --> 10:00.643
BECAUSE YESTERDAY

10:00.687 --> 10:03.472
I CAME HOME TO HELP
MY MOM AROUND THE HOUSE.

10:03.515 --> 10:05.256
MAC: DON'T WORRY,
HONEY.

10:05.300 --> 10:07.258
I'LL BE HOME SOON.

10:08.520 --> 10:10.522
I LOVE YOU, TOO.
BYE.

10:12.394 --> 10:14.352
HEY, WHO'S THAT?
HUH?

10:14.396 --> 10:17.660
OH, HO. HEY! CARL,
I WAS--I WAS JUST--

10:17.704 --> 10:20.794
CARL: NO, NO. WHO,
UH, WHO WAS THAT?

10:20.837 --> 10:23.144
IS EVERYTHING
ALL RIGHT?

10:23.187 --> 10:25.625
NO. HE JUST SAID
"I LOVE YOU"

10:25.668 --> 10:26.974
TO SOMEBODY ON THE PHONE.

10:27.017 --> 10:28.062
UH...

10:29.846 --> 10:31.282
YEAH, MY MOM.

10:31.326 --> 10:33.937
OH, YEAH? YOU CALL
YOUR MOTHER "HONEY"?

10:33.981 --> 10:35.417
YEAH, I DO.

10:35.460 --> 10:36.853
MONICA:
HE DOES.

10:36.897 --> 10:39.813
I'VE HEARD HIM.
HE CHECKS ON HER
SEVERAL TIMES A DAY.

10:39.856 --> 10:42.511
OK, HAVE YOU
EVER MET HIS MOTHER?

10:42.554 --> 10:43.991
NO, I HAVEN'T,
BUT--

10:44.034 --> 10:45.732
HEY, LET'S CLEAR THE AIR

10:45.775 --> 10:49.431
AND ADDRESS WHAT'S
REALLY GOING ON HERE, YEAH?

10:49.474 --> 10:52.652
YOU'RE BEING PROTECTIVE
OF YOUR MOM. HEH!

10:52.695 --> 10:54.131
AND AS YOU SHOULD,
BECAUSE SHE IS

10:54.175 --> 10:56.830
AN INCREDIBLY
SPECIAL WOMAN.

10:56.873 --> 10:58.396
BUT I WANT TO--

10:58.440 --> 11:00.094
I WANT TO PROVE TO YOU
HOW PURE MY INTENTIONS
ARE WITH HER,

11:00.137 --> 11:01.748
BECAUSE I KNOW
THIS HAS BEEN FAST.

11:01.791 --> 11:06.143
UM, I'VE BEEN WAITING
MY WHOLE LIFE FOR YOU...

11:08.102 --> 11:10.365
AND I DON'T WANT TO WAIT
ANY LONGER.

11:10.408 --> 11:12.236
WHAT?

11:12.280 --> 11:13.498
WHAT?

11:16.588 --> 11:18.025
WILL YOU MARRY ME?

11:18.068 --> 11:20.157
OH, OF COURSE
I WILL.

11:21.942 --> 11:23.508
IT'S BEAUTIFUL.

11:23.552 --> 11:24.945
I LOVE IT.

11:24.988 --> 11:26.729
CARL, VOICE-OVER: I COULDN'T
STAND WATCHING HER

11:26.773 --> 11:29.689
MAKE SUCH AN AWFUL DECISION
LIKE THAT, SO I LEFT.

11:29.732 --> 11:33.040
HE MUST'VE KILLED HER
AS SOON AS I WAS GONE.

11:33.083 --> 11:35.695
YOU HAVE ANY PHOTOS OF MAC?

11:37.958 --> 11:43.485
MY MOM, SHE POSTED A LOT
ON SOCIAL MEDIA.

11:43.528 --> 11:46.706
HERE'S ALL HIS
CONTACT INFO.

11:46.749 --> 11:49.273
ALVEZ: PAUL MacINTYRE,
AKA "MAC."

11:49.317 --> 11:52.059
HE DATED MONICA TWO MONTHS
BEFORE HE PROPOSED TO HER.

11:52.102 --> 11:53.843
AND THE ADDRESS HE GAVE HER
WAS A FAKE,

11:53.887 --> 11:56.063
AND THE PHONE NUMBER THAT HE
GAVE TO HER WAS

11:56.106 --> 11:57.847
FOR A BURNER THAT'S NOW
BEEN DISCONNECTED.

11:57.891 --> 11:59.240
REID: YOU KNOW, IT COULD BE
AN UNSUB WHO TARGETS

11:59.283 --> 12:00.981
A LONELY HEARTS
VICTIMOLOGY--

12:01.024 --> 12:03.940
MIDDLE-AGED WOMEN
WHO ARE EMOTIONALLY
SUSCEPTIBLE TO HIS CHARISMA.

12:03.984 --> 12:06.377
JAREAU: AND HE
TAKES HIS CHARM
AND HARM SEDUCTION

12:06.421 --> 12:07.944
ALL THE WAY UP
TO THE PROPOSAL

12:07.988 --> 12:08.989
AND KILLS THEM.

12:10.033 --> 12:11.774
PRENTISS: GARCIA,
WHAT'D YOU FIND?

12:11.818 --> 12:13.950
OK, I RAN THIS PHOTO
OF MR. MacINTYRE

12:13.994 --> 12:15.822
THROUGH FACIAL RECOGNITION,

12:15.865 --> 12:17.562
AND I'M TELLING YOU WITH
MY FULL CONFIDENCE

12:17.606 --> 12:18.825
HE DOES NOT EXIST.

12:18.868 --> 12:20.609
AND I WANT TO BE REALLY
CLEAR ABOUT THIS.

12:20.652 --> 12:22.176
I'M NOT SAYING HE
COVERED HIS TRACKS.

12:22.219 --> 12:24.526
I'M SAYING THIS GUY IS
A STONE-COLD APPARITION.

12:24.569 --> 12:26.180
IS THERE ANYTHING
IN THE CREATION OF
THE FALSE IDENTITY

12:26.223 --> 12:27.790
WE CAN TRACK?

12:27.834 --> 12:31.098
OK. ACCORDING TO HIS
FAUX DATING PROFILE,

12:31.141 --> 12:32.882
HE VALUES FAMILY
AND SERVING THE HOMELESS,

12:32.926 --> 12:34.231
WHICH WOULD BE REALLY
CUTE IF, YOU KNOW,

12:34.275 --> 12:36.712
HE DIDN'T CUT HER FACE OFF
AND BURN HER HOUSE DOWN.

12:36.756 --> 12:38.105
HELPING THE HOMELESS WAS

12:38.148 --> 12:39.846
EXACTLY WHAT MONICA
WAS INTERESTED IN.

12:39.889 --> 12:42.544
THE UNSUB WAS CREATING
A PERSONA TAILOR-MADE

12:42.587 --> 12:44.111
TO GET HER GUARD DOWN.

12:44.154 --> 12:45.808
WHAT ABOUT
FINANCIAL RECORDS?

12:45.852 --> 12:47.984
GARCIA: OH, THIS IS WHERE
THINGS GET REALLY NASTY.

12:48.028 --> 12:50.334
ACTUALLY, THE PART ABOUT
THE FACE IS THE NASTY THING,

12:50.378 --> 12:53.207
BUT I'M SENDING YOU
THE SPECIFICS ON THIS.

12:53.250 --> 12:55.992
SHORTLY BEFORE DATING
MONICA, THE UNSUB OPENED

12:56.036 --> 12:57.820
A BANK ACCOUNT USING
THIS FAKE IDENTITY.

12:57.864 --> 12:59.213
HE USED IT AS A FENCE
TO CREATE

12:59.256 --> 13:01.041
AN UNTRACEABLE
OFFSHORE ACCOUNT.

13:01.084 --> 13:03.695
HE WAS DRAINING MONICA'S
MONEY THE WHOLE TIME
THEY WERE DATING.

13:03.739 --> 13:05.828
GARCIA: AND THEN THE
LOW-DOWN, LYING SLEAZEBALL

13:05.872 --> 13:07.090
CLOSED SAID ACCOUNT.

13:07.134 --> 13:08.439
AND WE ALL KNOW
WHAT THAT MEANS,

13:08.483 --> 13:09.919
DON'T WE, MY PRETTIES?

13:09.963 --> 13:10.920
HE'S A CON MAN.

13:12.139 --> 13:13.009
LEWIS: YEAH, BUT CON MEN
RESORT TO VIOLENCE

13:13.053 --> 13:14.358
ONLY OUT OF NECESSITY.

13:14.402 --> 13:15.838
IF HE HAD A FALSE IDENTITY,

13:15.882 --> 13:17.057
IT WOULD HAVE BEEN EASIER
JUST TO SKIP TOWN

13:17.100 --> 13:18.580
THAN MURDER MONICA.

13:18.623 --> 13:20.712
MAYBE AFTER THE PROPOSAL,
MONICA DISCOVERED HE

13:20.756 --> 13:21.975
WASN'T WHO HE SAID HE WAS,

13:22.018 --> 13:24.847
AND THEN HE KILLED HER TO
PROTECT HIS ANONYMITY.

13:24.891 --> 13:26.980
BUT THEN WHY GO
TO THESE LENGTHS?

13:27.023 --> 13:28.329
WHY START THE FIRE?

13:28.372 --> 13:30.853
AND, MORE IMPORTANTLY,
WHY CUT OFF THE FACE?

13:30.897 --> 13:34.378
I WAS WONDERING
THAT, TOO.

13:34.422 --> 13:36.163
I MEAN, I'VE MET MY
SHARE OF CON MEN

13:36.206 --> 13:38.861
DEALING BLACKJACK
IN VEGAS,

13:38.905 --> 13:40.820
BUT ALL THEY CARE
ABOUT IS THE SCORE.

13:40.863 --> 13:42.822
EXACTLY. HIS RITUAL
DIDN'T MATCH

13:42.865 --> 13:44.562
WHAT A TYPICAL GRIFTER
WOULD DO.

13:44.606 --> 13:46.390
SO WHY GO THROUGH
ALL THAT STUFF

13:46.434 --> 13:48.175
WITH THE FACE
AND THE FIRE?

13:48.218 --> 13:49.393
WE WEREN'T SURE.

13:49.437 --> 13:50.917
AND WHILE WE WERE TRYING
TO FIGURE THAT OUT,

13:50.960 --> 13:52.614
HE'D ALREADY LEFT THE STATE...

13:54.834 --> 13:57.010
ROSSI, VOICE-OVER: AND DID WHAT
EVERY CON MAN DOES

13:57.053 --> 13:58.881
WHEN THEY'RE ON THE RUN.

14:00.491 --> 14:02.493
HE STARTED OVER.

14:47.843 --> 14:50.063
HOW ABOUT THIS?

14:50.106 --> 14:51.368
WOMAN: TURN TO THE LEFT.

14:51.412 --> 14:54.067
NOW TO THE RIGHT.

