IN A DOMESTIC DISPUTE.

28:45.158 --> 28:47.813
SOUNDS LIKE THAT RUNS
IN THE FAMILY, ALSO.

28:47.856 --> 28:51.077
KRYSTALL:
I IMAGINE A CON WOMAN

28:51.120 --> 28:53.906
WOULD BE
PRETTY TIGHT-LIPPED.

28:53.949 --> 28:56.299
THAT WAS
OUR ASSUMPTION, TOO,

28:56.343 --> 29:00.347
BUT SHE WASN'T QUITE
WHAT WE EXPECTED.

29:06.962 --> 29:09.312
WE APPRECIATE YOU SPEAKING
TO US, MRS. LYNCH.

29:09.356 --> 29:10.966
OH.

29:12.359 --> 29:15.928
MY DEGENERATE LAWYER
IS WHO TALKED ME INTO
THAT PLEA DEAL.

29:15.971 --> 29:18.321
NOW I'M STUCK
IN THIS BOX

29:18.365 --> 29:23.326
UNTIL I'LL BE...
SPORTIN' DEPENDS
UNDERNEATH THE JUMPSUIT.

29:25.111 --> 29:28.331
BUT IT ALSO MEANS
THAT I'M AN OPEN BOOK.

29:29.942 --> 29:31.900
OH.

29:33.946 --> 29:36.426
SORRY. SO WHAT CAN I DO
FOR YOU, BROWN EYES?

29:36.470 --> 29:38.428
MRS. LYNCH, WE, UH--

29:38.472 --> 29:41.431
OH, PLEASE.

29:41.475 --> 29:44.478
YOU GOT TO CALL
ME BOBBIE. HMM?

29:46.480 --> 29:49.831
BUT NOT YOU.
NOPE.

29:49.875 --> 29:52.834
YOU CALL ME
MS. LYNCH

29:52.878 --> 29:57.186
'CAUSE YOU'RE
A BAD, BAD BOY.

29:57.230 --> 30:00.842
I, UH, DON'T KNOW WHAT
TO SAY TO THAT.

30:00.886 --> 30:03.802
HA! STILL GOT IT.

30:03.845 --> 30:04.977
BOBBIE,

30:05.020 --> 30:07.370
WE'RE HERE TO TALK
TO YOU ABOUT EVERETT.

30:07.414 --> 30:09.677
YEAH, ALL RIGHT.
THAT DOESN'T
SURPRISE ME.

30:09.720 --> 30:11.505
WHEN WAS THE LAST TIME
YOU SAW HIM?

30:11.548 --> 30:15.117
THAT KID'S BEEN
IN THE WIND
SINCE HE WAS...

30:15.161 --> 30:18.120
22 OR...

30:18.164 --> 30:21.515
AND HE'S NEVER
REACHED OUT. HEH!

30:21.558 --> 30:25.127
HE NEVER EVEN CAME
TO VISIT ME.

30:25.171 --> 30:27.521
YOU TELL ME,
WHAT KIND OF SON

30:27.564 --> 30:30.132
TREATS HIS MAMA
THAT WAY?

30:30.176 --> 30:32.526
ESPECIALLY AFTER
EVERYTHING THAT I
TAUGHT HIM.

30:32.569 --> 30:34.354
WHAT DID YOU TEACH HIM?

30:34.397 --> 30:36.356
WELL, HE WAS
MY LITTLE SOLDIER.

30:36.399 --> 30:40.229
HE WAS...
MY PARTNER IN CRIME.

30:40.273 --> 30:42.971
WE WERE JUST
A COUPLE OF
ROLLING STONES,

30:43.015 --> 30:45.365
MAKING
OUR WAY ACROSS
THE BIBLE BELT.

30:45.408 --> 30:47.758
YOU'RE TALKING
ABOUT YOUR CONS, RIGHT?

30:49.804 --> 30:52.241
THAT'S RIGHT, MUSCLES.

30:52.285 --> 30:56.985
SEE, I WOULD FIND
SOME GULLIBLE SCHMO...

30:59.379 --> 31:04.253
AND I'D TELL HIM
HOW WE...

31:04.297 --> 31:08.997
I WAS THROWN OUT
ON THE STREET
WITH MY POOR KID.

31:10.390 --> 31:12.958
YOU KNOW, NOTHING
OPENS UP DOORS

31:13.001 --> 31:15.612
LIKE A BLUBBERING
7-YEAR-OLD,
I TELL YA. HA!

31:15.656 --> 31:18.398
THEY WOULD FALL ASS
OVER ELBOWS, JUST--

31:18.441 --> 31:22.271
AND THEN,
PRETTY SOON...

31:22.315 --> 31:23.925
THEY'D GET DOWN
ON ONE KNEE

31:23.969 --> 31:27.189
AND I WOULD JUST
TAKE 'EM FOR EVERY
LAST NICKEL.

31:27.233 --> 31:29.757
THEN YOU KNOW WHAT
WOULD HAPPEN?

31:29.800 --> 31:31.324
WHAT?

31:33.369 --> 31:36.329
WE'D LAUGH.

31:36.372 --> 31:39.941
OH, MY, WE WOULD
LAUGH SO MUCH JUST

31:39.985 --> 31:43.423
ABOUT THESE POOR,
HELPLESS CHUMPS. HA!

31:43.466 --> 31:45.816
WHERE DO YOU THINK EVERETT
MIGHT BE RIGHT NOW?

31:45.860 --> 31:48.428
I DON'T KNOW.
I GOT NO IDEA.

31:48.471 --> 31:52.780
BUT--HEH!--GIVEN
THAT THE FEDS ARE
LOOKIN' FOR HIM,

31:52.823 --> 31:56.566
I SURMISE THAT HE'S
STILL RUNNIN' CONS,

31:56.610 --> 31:58.525
AND GUESS WHAT.

31:58.568 --> 32:01.093
YOU'RE NEVER GONNA
CATCH HIM

32:01.136 --> 32:03.051
'CAUSE I TAUGHT HIM
EVERYTHING I KNOW,

32:03.095 --> 32:05.053
EVERYTHING,
AND THAT IS ENOUGH
TO KEEP HIM

32:05.097 --> 32:08.317
ALWAYS JUST OUT
OF YOUR REACH.

32:08.361 --> 32:10.929
HE'S KILLING
HIS MARKS NOW.

32:10.972 --> 32:13.540
ALVEZ: BUT WE THINK
HE'S DOING IT

32:13.583 --> 32:16.151
BECAUSE HE CAN'T
KILL YOU...

32:16.195 --> 32:19.154
AFTER WHAT YOU DID
TO GRACE.

32:19.198 --> 32:22.201
GRACE?YEAH, YOUR GRANDDAUGHTER.

32:22.244 --> 32:25.160
THE ONE YOU LET DROWN,
YOU WERE SUPPOSED TO BE
WATCHING HER?

32:35.518 --> 32:39.914
TOOK AWAY MY UTENSILS,
JUST 'CAUSE I SHIVVED SOME
PRETTY BITCH LAST SUMMER.

32:43.048 --> 32:46.399
FORGIVE ME, AGENTS,
BUT...

32:46.442 --> 32:50.011
I THINK THAT I'VE
ANSWERED ENOUGH
OF YOUR QUESTIONS.

32:50.055 --> 32:52.709
JAREAU: THE DETAIL
ABOUT THE DROWNING HIT
A NERVE WITH ROBERTA.

32:52.753 --> 32:56.452
WHICH SUGGESTS THERE'S
ANOTHER ELEMENT OF TRUTH
TO EVERETT'S BACK STORY.

32:56.496 --> 32:59.455
NOW, HE PUTS HIMSELF
IN THE SUBMISSIVE ROLE

32:59.499 --> 33:02.545
THAT HE AND HIS MOTHER
WOULD TAKE ADVANTAGE OF
IN HER CONS.

33:02.589 --> 33:04.547
SO EVERY TIME HE
GETS DOWN ON ONE KNEE
WITH HIS VICTIMS,

33:04.591 --> 33:06.332
HE HEARS
HIS MOTHER'S LAUGHTER
RINGING IN HIS EARS.

33:06.375 --> 33:09.030
ROBERTA SAID
THAT SHE TAUGHT EVERETT
EVERYTHING HE KNOWS.

33:09.074 --> 33:11.032
WHAT IF THERE'S
A PATTERN IN THAT?

33:11.076 --> 33:12.381
PRENTISS:
WHAT KIND OF PATTERN?

33:12.425 --> 33:14.340
FOLLOWING
HER TRAIL, MAYBE,
GOING TO THE CITIES

33:14.383 --> 33:17.691
WHERE HER CON WORKED,
THINKING HE CAN WORK
THE SAME MAGIC.

33:17.734 --> 33:19.693
HEY, ROSSI'S RIGHT.
ALL 3 OF EVERETT'S KILLS

33:19.736 --> 33:22.304
HAPPENED IN CITIES WHERE
HIS MOM CONNED A MAN:

33:22.348 --> 33:25.220
BIRMINGHAM, MEMPHIS,
NASHVILLE.

33:25.264 --> 33:27.875
HE'S EVEN MIRRORING
THE ORDER IN WHICH HIS
MOTHER VISITED EACH CITY.

33:27.918 --> 33:30.008
WHERE DID ROBERTA GO
AFTER NASHVILLE?
LITTLE ROCK.

33:30.051 --> 33:32.271
WELL, THAT'S GOT TO BE
WHERE HE IS NOW.

33:35.752 --> 33:38.320
I WAS GETTING LONELY.
WHAT DO YOU NEED?

33:38.364 --> 33:40.540
WE THINK OUR UNSUB'S
NEXT TARGET LIVES
IN LITTLE ROCK.

33:40.583 --> 33:42.542
I NEED YOU
TO ASSEMBLE A POOL
OF POTENTIAL VICTIMS

33:42.585 --> 33:44.935
BASED ON OUR
VICTIMOLOGY--WOMEN
ROUGHLY 50 YEARS OLD,

33:44.979 --> 33:48.548
RECENT EMPTY-NESTERS.NO BOUT A DOUBT IT.

33:48.591 --> 33:50.724
JAREAU: LIMIT
YOUR SEARCH TO WOMEN
ON DATING WEBSITES,

33:50.767 --> 33:52.943
SPECIFICALLY THOSE
INTERESTED IN
GETTING MARRIED.

33:52.987 --> 33:56.817
OK, WOMEN IN LITTLE ROCK
LOOKING FOR...A LITTLE ROCK.

33:56.860 --> 33:58.862
PRENTISS: SEND US
THEIR DATING PROFILES
AND SOCIAL MEDIA.

33:58.906 --> 34:01.474
WE'LL WORK IT ON OUR END.YEAH, YEAH.

34:01.517 --> 34:05.173
KRYSTALL: THAT MUST
HAVE BEEN A LONG LIST
OF POTENTIAL VICTIMS.

34:05.217 --> 34:09.090
ROSSI: REID DOES HAVE A KNACK
OF FINDING THE BLACK CAT
IN THE COAL MINE.

34:09.134 --> 34:11.136
GOT HIM.

34:15.531 --> 34:19.187
AND THAT'S HOW YOU
CAUGHT HIM, FINALLY.

34:19.231 --> 34:22.582
NO, IT IS HOW WE
FOUND HIM,

34:22.625 --> 34:25.585
BUT WHAT WE
DIDN'T KNOW WAS THAT
THE UNSUB'S MOTHER

34:25.628 --> 34:28.544
MADE A PHONE CALL
FROM THE PRISON
AFTER WE LEFT.

34:28.588 --> 34:29.545
TO HER SON.

34:29.589 --> 34:31.156
TO HER LAWYER,

34:31.199 --> 34:33.158
AND SINCE
THAT'S PRIVILEGED,
WE DON'T KNOW

34:33.201 --> 34:36.770
EXACTLY WHAT SHE
SAID, BUT WE CAN
HAZARD A GUESS.

34:36.813 --> 34:38.772
YOU TELL
THAT ROTTEN BASTARD

34:38.815 --> 34:42.384
THAT THE FBI IS
ON HIS ASS,

34:42.428 --> 34:44.778
AND HOW DARE HE,

34:44.821 --> 34:49.826
HOW DARE HE BRING
MY GRANDDAUGHTER
INTO HIS...

34:51.437 --> 34:53.874
AND THAT'S NOT MY FAULT.

34:53.917 --> 34:55.876
HE DID WHAT HE DID

34:55.919 --> 34:59.880
TO--TO POOR LITTLE GRACIE.
THAT'S NOT ON ME.

34:59.923 --> 35:03.492
ROSSI: BECAUSE OF THAT, WE LOST
THE ELEMENT OF SURPRISE.

35:03.536 --> 35:05.929
SHE SAID WHAT?

35:08.149 --> 35:10.108
OK.

35:10.151 --> 35:13.633
I'M GONNA NEED
TO IMPROVISE
A LITTLE BIT,

35:13.676 --> 35:15.417
OK?

35:17.027 --> 35:19.639
SO HERE'S WHAT
WE'RE GONNA DO.

35:24.034 --> 35:26.907
SO YOU WERE WALKING
INTO A TRAP.

35:28.517 --> 35:30.476
I...

35:30.519 --> 35:33.696
I CAN'T LEAVE
THIS NEXT PART TO
THE IMAGINATION.

35:33.740 --> 35:36.743
IT'S OK. JUST--
JUST TAKE YOUR TIME.

35:44.707 --> 35:47.101
ROSSI, VOICE-OVER:
WE UNDERESTIMATED.

35:49.625 --> 35:51.801
KRYSTALL: UNDERESTIMATED WHAT?

36:01.550 --> 36:03.944
ROSSI: HOW MANY WOMEN HE KILLED.

36:20.569 --> 36:22.963
SO...

36:25.183 --> 36:27.489
WITH THOSE FIRST
3 VICTIMS...

36:27.533 --> 36:30.492
ROSSI, VOICE-OVER: WE WERE
BARELY SCRATCHING THE SURFACE.

36:30.536 --> 36:33.495
ONCE WE WERE INSIDE THE HOUSE,
WE HEARD HER SCREAMING.

36:33.539 --> 36:35.410
HELP! HELP ME!
UPSTAIRS.

36:35.454 --> 36:37.195
WE NEED TO CLEAR
THE BACK OF THE HOUSE.

36:37.238 --> 36:38.718
I'M WITH YOU. GO.KRYSTALL: WHO, THE MOTHER?

36:38.761 --> 36:41.938
ROSSI: THE DAUGHTER.PLEASE, YOU GOT TO HELP ME!

36:41.982 --> 36:43.984
HEY, DON'T WORRY.
WE'RE GONNA GET YOU
OUT OF HERE.

36:44.027 --> 36:46.247
HE TOOK HER!
YOU HAVE TO SAVE HER!

36:46.291 --> 36:48.206
REID: NO SIGN OF HIM
OR MARY. LEWIS IS
WITH ROSSI AND SIMMONS.

36:48.249 --> 36:49.990
WHERE DID HE TAKE
YOUR MOM?

36:50.033 --> 36:51.992
THERE'S A BARN
IN THE WOODS OUT BACK!

36:52.035 --> 36:55.038
ROSSI, CHECK THE WOODS
BEHIND THE HOUSE.
LOOK FOR A BARN.

37:07.181 --> 37:08.530
WE GOT YOU.

37:11.229 --> 37:13.753
IT DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.
THE FACES ARE HIS TROPHIES.

37:13.796 --> 37:15.755
HE WOULDN'T LEAVE THEM
BEHIND IF--

37:15.798 --> 37:18.018
HE KNEW WE WERE COMING.PLEASE!

37:18.061 --> 37:19.976
YOU HAVE TO FIND HER!

37:20.020 --> 37:22.544
DON'T WORRY. WE'RE GONNA
FIND YOUR MOM. ALL RIGHT,
NOW WHAT'S YOUR NAME?

37:22.588 --> 37:25.155
GRACE. I'M GRACE. PLEASE!
HE'S GONNA KILL HER!

37:25.199 --> 37:26.896
GRACE?

37:28.028 --> 37:30.509
DADDY!

37:32.337 --> 37:34.295
OH, MY GOD.

37:34.339 --> 37:36.341
SHE WAS HIS DAUGHTER?

37:36.384 --> 37:38.343
YES.

37:38.386 --> 37:40.997
MARY CULLEN DID HAVE
A COLLEGE-AGE DAUGHTER,

37:41.041 --> 37:43.043
BUT SHE WAS AT COLLEGE.

37:43.086 --> 37:45.828
GRACE NEVER DROWNED?
NO.

37:45.872 --> 37:49.876
AND THIS WAS THE FIRST
TIME HE BROUGHT HER IN
ON ONE OF HIS CONS.

37:52.357 --> 37:54.924
WE DIDN'T SEE IT,

37:54.968 --> 37:57.971
AND IT ALMOST GOT US
ALL KILLED.

38:01.583 --> 38:04.151
SIMMONS: FIND OUT WHERE
HE'S SHOOTING FROM!

38:11.941 --> 38:14.640
ROSSI: TAKE THE OTHER SIDE.
I'M GOING TO TRY TO FLANK
HIM FROM BEHIND.

38:14.683 --> 38:16.076
YEAH.

39:03.428 --> 39:07.040
ROSSI, VOICE-OVER:
MY LAST THOUGHT WAS,
"DON'T BLACK OUT.

39:07.083 --> 39:09.695
IF YOU BLACK OUT,
YOU'RE DEAD."

39:14.700 --> 39:16.702
AND THEN I BLACKED OUT.

39:21.271 --> 39:25.232
WE SAVED MARY,
WE ARRESTED GRACE,

39:25.275 --> 39:27.582
BUT HE GOT AWAY.

39:27.626 --> 39:30.237
YOU'LL CATCH HIM.

39:30.280 --> 39:33.066
EXCEPT THIS GUY,
HE'S A CHAMELEON.

39:33.109 --> 39:37.287
HE COULD WALK UP TO ME
WITH A GUN IN HIS HAND AND
I'D NEVER SEE HIM COMING.

39:37.331 --> 39:39.246
THAT'S WHERE THIS
CAME FROM.

39:41.291 --> 39:45.252
ROSSI, VOICE-OVER:
HE LEFT ME A REMINDER
OF WHAT HE COULD DO.

39:45.295 --> 39:48.168
HE COULD HAVE TAKEN
MY FACE IF HE WANTED.

39:48.211 --> 39:50.170
HE DIDN'T.

39:50.213 --> 39:54.740
YOU KNOW, SOMETIMES YOU
LOSE ON THIS JOB.

39:54.783 --> 39:59.179
I GET IT, BUT THIS IS
THE FIRST TIME
IN A LONG TIME

39:59.222 --> 40:02.182
THAT I WAS BEATEN BY
SOMEONE YOUNGER, FASTER,

40:02.225 --> 40:04.358
STRONGER THAN I AM.

40:05.968 --> 40:10.320
BUT THAT'S WHAT'S
BEEN BOTHERING ME
ABOUT THIS CASE...

40:11.931 --> 40:14.281
THAT MAYBE I'M...

40:14.324 --> 40:17.893
JUST NOT AS GOOD
AS I ONCE WAS.

40:17.937 --> 40:22.898
MAYBE I'M A HALF A STEP
SLOWER, MAYBE...

40:22.942 --> 40:26.902
MAYBE I SHOULDN'T
BE OUT THERE

40:26.946 --> 40:30.340
BECAUSE NEXT TIME...

40:31.951 --> 40:34.954
NEXT TIME,
I WON'T WAKE UP.

40:36.390 --> 40:38.697
YOU LEFT
SOMETHING OUT.

40:38.740 --> 40:41.700
YOU DIDN'T SAY SMARTER

40:41.743 --> 40:44.703
BECAUSE HE ISN'T,

40:44.746 --> 40:47.488
AND THAT'S HOW YOU'RE
GONNA CATCH HIM

40:47.532 --> 40:50.491
BECAUSE THAT'S HOW YOU
ALWAYS CATCH 'EM.

40:50.535 --> 40:53.581
YOU'RE NOT THE ONLY ONE
THAT LOST.

40:55.235 --> 40:57.455
HE LOST, TOO.

41:00.283 --> 41:03.591
AND EVEN I KNOW

41:03.635 --> 41:06.594
WHERE YOU HAVE TO GO NEXT.

41:11.599 --> 41:14.210
THANK YOU

41:14.254 --> 41:16.430
FOR LISTENING...

41:18.040 --> 41:20.390
FOR...

41:20.434 --> 41:23.437
FOR BEING HERE.

41:28.050 --> 41:30.052
DO YOU WANT ME
TO GO WITH YOU?

41:30.096 --> 41:32.098
NO.

41:33.491 --> 41:37.320
I'VE GOT TO DO
THIS ONE ON MY OWN.

42:01.519 --> 42:04.522
LET'S TALK
ABOUT YOUR FATHER.

